title: Queen & Country (Oni Press)
description:
Queen & Country is the Eisner Award-winning and critically lauded espionage series from acclaimed novelist and comic book author Greg Rucka. 

SIS field agent Tara Chase is sent all over the world in service to her Queen & Country all the while Director of Operations Paul Crocker walks a narrow tightrope between his loyalty to his people and the political masters that must be served.


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
